* Interface notes
** `forEach`
   `option = alloy.module.forEach (host: { ... })`
** Self
   `alloy` arg has a special `self` field that contains this host expanded.
** Remote extend
   @code nix
   { config, ... }: {
     alloy.extend.nginx = [({ alloy, ... }: {
       services.nginx.virtualHosts.web-server = {
         proxyPass = "${alloy.self.address}:${toString config.services.web-server.port}";
       };
     })];
     services.web-server.enable = true;
   }
   @end
** Middleware
   @code nix
   {
     middleware = alloy-utils.mkMiddleware { ... };

     hosts = mods: {
       pc = {
         modules = [];
         region = "home";
       };
       laptop = {
         modules = [];
         region = "roaming";
       };
     };
   }
   @end
